Implementation of 'Template-based IE without the Templates' on Tweets
==============================================
Authors: Yanxia Qin

contact: qolina@gmail.com

Example Usage:
-------------
1. Preprocess tweet text file (non-Eng tweets filtering, normalization)
2. NER+POS (twitter NLP tools by Alan Ritter)
Average time per tweet = 0.0535215378005s

3. extracting event patterns (POS-tagged, NE recognized tweet text + wordNet Event synset noun dictionary)

4. event pattern clustering
...4.1 LDA clustering
       LDA tool : GibbsLDA++-0.2 from http://sourceforge.net/projects/gibbslda/ 

...4.2 Agglomerative clustering
       self implemented
